data.title: Thailand's reformist Move Forward Party, dissolved by court order, regroups as People's Party
data.meta_description: Just two days after being disbanded by court order, Thailand's main progressive political party regrouped Friday under a new name and vowed to continue its fight for reforms despite continuing opposition from the conservative establishment that blocked the party from taking power despite finishing first in last year's election.
data.text:
Just two days after being disbanded by court order, Thailand's main progressive political party regrouped Friday under a new name and vowed to continue its fight for reforms despite continuing opposition from the conservative establishment that blocked the party from taking power despite finishing first in last year's election.

By JINTAMAS SAKSORNCHAI

Associated Press

August 9, 2024 at 8:36AM
